{
  "stem": "71.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were other people that spoke German-- I think somebody said-- somebody said that-- that her mother suffered from gallstones.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And either it was true or not.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who knows?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was probably an interesting thing that she must have loved her mother very much.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when they were-- it was time for us to leave when-- when the Russians came closer to-- to [?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Camitz, ?] she came into dispensary, and she says, I want you to stay here, because you'll never make this march.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I told her that I have two sisters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I says, if my sisters can stay here with me, then I stay.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If not, I go on the march.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my sisters were carrying me to the train, actually carrying me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because I could not walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after the wall, we--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, she didn't help me, but she also was not against it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I would have stayed, I would have been liberated on the 22nd of April.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the Russians came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we went on a train, and we're going back and forth and being bombarded on the train.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We came to-- to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then when we were waiting, the Red Cross was that time in Theresienstadt, and they were not even interested when they were leaving.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They saw 500 girls staying outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were not even interested to come over and ask, what are these women doing here?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we waited till they left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then they admitted us to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember, like she had a girl that used to polish her shoes, her boots.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she put her-- her foot on a stump on a tree and said to the girl, now, Helenka, who is going to polish my boots from now on?",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
